# Graphify (canonical — all agents read this; do not duplicate in AGENTS.md prose)

Local knowledge graph: `graphify-out/` (gitignored forever). Install: `py -3.12 -m pip install graphifyy`.

## Query-first (Consultant / Otto / Auto — read-only)

When `graphify-out/graph.json` exists, before broad grep or reading many files:

```bash
py -3.12 -m graphify query "<narrow question>"
py -3.12 -m graphify path "<A>" "<B>"
py -3.12 -m graphify explain "<concept>"
```

- Never load `graph.json` into context (~24k nodes; machine-only).
- `GRAPH_REPORT.md`: read only **Corpus/Summary**, **Graph Freshness**, **God Nodes**, **Surprising Connections**, **Suggested Questions**. Skip Community Hubs and Communities.
- If `graphify-out/wiki/index.md` exists, use it instead of raw file spelunking.
- May run `python3 scripts/check_graphify_freshness.py` (no `--strict`) to report staleness.
- **Must not** run `graphify update`, `graphify site`, or commit `graphify-out/`.

## Graph refresh (user + Cline — after graph-relevant edits)

**Graph refresh** = re-extract AST and rebuild the local graph (no LLM cost):

```bash
py -3.12 -m graphify update .
```

Run when you change lesson `code/`, `docs/`, `outputs/`, or anything under `site/`.

**Skip graph refresh** when the session only touched README, ROADMAP, glossary, or `phases/**/quiz.json` (no `code/`, no `site/`).

Optional long sessions: `py -3.12 -m graphify watch .` (continuous refresh on save).

Do **not** run `graphify site` on this repo — full graph exceeds HTML viz limits; use query/path/explain.

## Freshness gate (Cline / implementer — hard exit after refresh)

After graph refresh (or when graph-relevant files changed vs HEAD):

```bash
python3 scripts/check_graphify_freshness.py --strict
```

Exit **0** required before marking the task done. Exit **1** = stale → run graph refresh again.

Checker skips automatically for quiz-only / catalog-only work unless you pass `--always`.

## Do not

- Add CI, pre-commit hooks, or `.cursor/hooks.json` for graphify (agent-side rule + script only).
- Run `graphify cursor install` here — it overwrites this file with the stock template.
- Commit `graphify-out/` or use Obsidian/wiki unless the user explicitly asks later.

## Quick reference

| Who | Explore | Refresh graph | Verify |
|-----|---------|---------------|--------|
| User (Raymo) | query / path / explain | **graph refresh**: `graphify update .` | optional: `check_graphify_freshness.py --always` |
| Otto | query only | never | optional, no `--strict` |
| Cline | query when reviewing | update after code/site edits | `--strict` must pass |
